<subSubSection id="9EEF6552FFA00C20B9E0E1D4D088FE5B" pageId="8" pageNumber="51" type="distribution">
<paragraph id="D64A36D9FFA00C20B9E0E1D4D000FE97" blockId="8.[151,1437,150,536]" pageId="8" pageNumber="51">
<emphasis id="E481EACBFFA00C20B9E0E1D4D009FF3A" bold="true" box="[199,599,150,176]" pageId="8" pageNumber="51">Distribution and notes on biology.</emphasis>
<taxonomicName id="11F54D5AFFA00C20BB7AE1D4D161FF3A" authorityName="Turan &amp; Kottelat &amp; Kaya" authorityYear="2022" box="[605,831,150,176]" class="Actinopterygii" family="Salmonidae" genus="Salmo" kingdom="Animalia" order="Salmoniformes" pageId="8" pageNumber="51" phylum="Chordata" rank="species" species="ardahanensis">
<emphasis id="E481EACBFFA00C20BB7AE1D4D161FF3A" box="[605,831,150,176]" italics="true" pageId="8" pageNumber="51">Salmo ardahanensis</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
is known from the upper Kura River drainage (
<figureCitation id="4ECE2A5CFFA00C20BC6CE1D4D7D0FF3A" box="[1355,1422,150,176]" captionStart="FIGURE 3" captionStartId="5.[151,250,1476,1500]" captionTargetBox="[228,1360,814,1451]" captionTargetId="figure-342@5.[227,1361,813,1452]" captionTargetPageId="5" captionText="FIGURE 3. Map of eastern Anatolia showing the distribution of the native Salmo specimens examined for this study." figureDoi="http://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.6609949" httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/6609949/files/figure.png" pageId="8" pageNumber="51">Fig. 3</figureCitation>
). 
<taxonomicName id="11F54D5AFFA00C20B9B0E1F8D325FF5E" authorityName="Turan &amp; Kottelat &amp; Kaya" authorityYear="2022" box="[151,379,186,212]" class="Actinopterygii" family="Salmonidae" genus="Salmo" kingdom="Animalia" order="Salmoniformes" pageId="8" pageNumber="51" phylum="Chordata" rank="species" species="ardahanensis">
<emphasis id="E481EACBFFA00C20B9B0E1F8D325FF5E" box="[151,379,186,212]" italics="true" pageId="8" pageNumber="51">Salmo ardahanensis</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
was observed in clear and fast flowing water, with stone and pebble bottom. The species has never been observed in the lower part of the streams. The maximum size observed in the field is 
<quantity id="110D9B3CFFA00C20BD9AE19CD747FF73" box="[1213,1305,222,249]" metricMagnitude="-1" metricUnit="m" metricValue="2.8" pageId="8" pageNumber="51" unit="mm" value="280.0">280 mm</quantity>
SL. Mature individuals were observed in both sexes.
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="D64A36D9FFA00C20B9E0E064D088FE5B" blockId="8.[151,1437,150,536]" pageId="8" pageNumber="51">
<taxonomicName id="11F54D5AFFA00C20B9E0E064D3F5FECA" authorityName="Turan &amp; Kottelat &amp; Kaya" authorityYear="2022" box="[199,427,294,320]" class="Actinopterygii" family="Salmonidae" genus="Salmo" kingdom="Animalia" order="Salmoniformes" pageId="8" pageNumber="51" phylum="Chordata" rank="species" species="ardahanensis">
<emphasis id="E481EACBFFA00C20B9E0E064D3F5FECA" box="[199,427,294,320]" italics="true" pageId="8" pageNumber="51">Salmo ardahanensis</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
is a resident trouts apparently restricted to the 
<location id="D32A6002FFA00C20BAE7E065D6D8FECA" LSID="urn:lsid:plazi:treatment:5E5C87CFFFAD0C20B9B0E7A3D373FD92:D32A6002FFA00C20BAE7E065D6D8FECA" box="[960,1158,294,321]" county="Kura River" latitude="41.133335" longLatPrecision="1158" longitude="42.85" municipality="Asikzulal" name="upper Kura River" pageId="8" pageNumber="51">upper Kura River</location>
drainage. 
<location id="D32A6002FFA00C20BDDAE065D77CFECB" LSID="urn:lsid:plazi:treatment:5E5C87CFFFAD0C20B9B0E7A3D373FD92:D32A6002FFA00C20BDDAE065D77CFECB" box="[1277,1314,295,321]" county="Kura River" latitude="41.133335" longLatPrecision="1158" longitude="42.85" municipality="Asikzulal" name="We" pageId="8" pageNumber="51">We</location>
conducted field work during both summer and late autumn and we did not observe any migratory form of the species in the 
<location id="D32A6002FFA00C20B9B0E02CD2B3FE02" LSID="urn:lsid:plazi:treatment:5E5C87CFFFAD0C20B9B0E7A3D373FD92:D32A6002FFA00C20B9B0E02CD2B3FE02" box="[151,237,366,392]" county="Kura River" latitude="41.133335" longLatPrecision="1158" longitude="42.85" municipality="Asikzulal" name="Turkish" pageId="8" pageNumber="51">Turkish</location>
part of 
<location id="D32A6002FFA00C20B860E02DD399FE02" LSID="urn:lsid:plazi:treatment:5E5C87CFFFAD0C20B9B0E7A3D373FD92:D32A6002FFA00C20B860E02DD399FE02" box="[327,455,366,393]" county="Kura River" latitude="41.133335" longLatPrecision="1158" longitude="42.85" municipality="Asikzulal" name="Kura River" pageId="8" pageNumber="51">Kura River</location>
, including in relatively larger streams at lower altitude (e.g. stream 
<collectingMunicipality id="362EACA3FFA00C20BDE5E02CD76EFE02" box="[1218,1328,366,392]" pageId="8" pageNumber="51">Aşıkzülal</collectingMunicipality>
, 
<geoCoordinate id="B3C1501EFFA00C20BC1CE02CD7C2FE02" box="[1339,1436,366,392]" degrees="41" direction="north" minutes="26" orientation="latitude" pageId="8" pageNumber="51" precision="925" value="41.433334">41°26’N</geoCoordinate>
<geoCoordinate id="B3C1501EFFA00C20B9B0E0D0D2A9FE26" box="[151,247,402,428]" degrees="42" direction="east" minutes="37" orientation="longitude" pageId="8" pageNumber="51" precision="925" value="42.616665">42°37’E</geoCoordinate>
, altitude 
<quantity id="110D9B3CFFA00C20B87BE0D0D3EDFE27" box="[348,435,402,429]" metricMagnitude="3" metricUnit="m" metricValue="1.8" pageId="8" pageNumber="51" unit="m" value="1800.0">
